 need to wait after performing appropriate actions

Implicit wait - cannot locate an object immediately because of its unavailability

 //Puts a Implicit wait, Will wait for 10 seconds before throwing exception
      driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(10, TimeUnit.SECONDS);


 'explicit wait,' waits for a certain condition to occur before proceeding further. It is mainly used when we want to click or act on an object once it is visible
 
 
 Fluent wait - timer and need check constant
